Class ChannelConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ef.cim.objectmodel.ChannelConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Valid
public class ChannelConfig
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A ChannelConfig object represents the configurations for a specific channel (e.g. mode, sLAs, routing policy e.t.c.)
